<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.6.9">
<l>entāy taṇṭiru vēṅkaṭattu ṇiṉṟā yilaṅkai ceṟṟāy marāmaram</l>
<l>paintā ḷēḻuruva voruvāḷi kōtta villā</l>
<l>kontār taṇṇan tuḻāyiṉā yamutē yuṉṉai yeṉṉuḷḷē kuḻaittavem</l>
<l>maintā vāṉēṟē yiṉiyeṅku pōkiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our father, you who stand on cool, sacred Vēṅkaṭam, you who destroyed Laṅka, bowman</l>
<l>who strung a shapely arrow [against] seven green trunks of the Cadamba trees,</l>
<l>you with cool Tulsi full of flower clusters, ambrosia, young man of us who mixed you</l>
<l>into my heart, bull of heaven, where is there to go now?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
